  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7, then boil a kettle and take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet to let it and let it air</p><p>Add your <strong>ground cumin,</strong> <strong>ground</strong> <strong>smoked paprika</strong> and <strong>chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and mix until combined</p><p>Add your <strong>free</strong> <strong>range</strong> <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to the plate and turn them several times until evenly coated in all the spices</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1517.-step-1-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
