    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>tomato paste</strong> in 200ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml]</span> [375ml]</span> <strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> tomato stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
