    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>cannellini beans</strong>, <strong>tomato stock</strong> and <strong>chicken thighs</strong> to an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong> and put the dish in the oven for 25-35 min or until the chicken is cooked through (no pink meat!)</p>",
